prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon pizza slice, wearing a tiny party hat askew on its crust, is doing an exaggerated, clumsy yoga pose (like the Tree Pose, but wobbly). Its pepperoni eyes are wide with comical strain, and a tiny sweat drop flies off its cheesy face. Below the pizza, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the word "birthday". The entire scene is rendered as a flat 2D watercolor painting, with soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the pizza and text.
